		<official-title>To amend <external-xref legal-doc="usc-chapter" parsable-cite="usc-chapter/18/44">chapter 44</external-xref> of title 18, United States Code, to prohibit the possession of a firearm by a
			 person who is adjudicated to have committed a violent juvenile act.</official-title>
